{"tid":1253372,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為高層確認 Mate X 上市日期  肯定會預載 Android 系統","createTime":"2019-06-23T14:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T15:32:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"923678a5be8032208d07dd6c7612c69e2d872dd9","tid":1253372,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"華為西歐地區總裁 Vincent Pang 日前接受訪問，確認摺機 Mate X 將會在最遲 9 月推出，他保證 9 月一定能夠上市，亦有提前推出的可能性。至於 Mate X 會在甚麼地方發售，Vincent 表示任何有 5G 網絡的地區，至於只有 4G 的地方會否上市，他則未有言明。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2019-06/23/213369/uniqlo_1_fb201dadcda961bf58777dd5376db01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-06%2F23%2F213369%2Funiqlo_1_fb201dadcda961bf58777dd5376db01a.jpg&h=e9cb4091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信最多消費者想知道的，就是華為會否在 Mate X 如在自家鴻蒙系統。根據 Vincent Pang 的說法，是因為 Mate X 在美國商務部公佈黑名單前發表，所以不受禁令影響，將會預載 Android 系統。Vincent 又表示將上市日期設定在 9 月，是為了進行大量測試，確保柔性可摺 P-OLED 屏幕不會像 Samsung Galaxy Fold 般出問題，不過事實是否如此，還要留待正式推出時才有答案。"},{"pid":"8e989e9becb5db1a425a158ddd4f57fcb1506a0a","tid":1253372,"uid":140218,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:08:52.000Z","msg":"不過無得Update <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e543f85a346f49a849889b1b165dbb0a11a0447","tid":1253372,"uid":149959,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"吹到鴻蒙天下無敵<br />\n點唔用鴻蒙要用垃圾android<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75100726a65ca91e4e6b0315c7a84ccf7cdec8e4","tid":1253372,"uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T18:25:58.000Z","msg":"外國邊個會買?<br />\n大陸D有錢佬又唔敢買呢D外國勢力既系統"},{"pid":"99f9e36ee1d227162d0aff045cf2cf2efdbb2179","tid":1253372,"uid":216417,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3e543f85a346f49a849889b1b165dbb0a11a0447","tid":1253372,"uid":149959,"lik